#: ui/MainWindow.glade:5172
msgid "Try Fix"
msgstr "Tente corrigir"

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:5214
msgid ""
"This operation;\n"
"will remove all sources.list and sources.list.d entries and create "
"defaults,\n"
"will run \"apt update\" command,\n"
"will run \"apt install --fix-broken\" command,\n"
"will run \"dpkg --configure -a\".\n"
"\n"
"Use with caution. Are you sure you want to continue?"
msgstr ""
"Esta operação;\n"
"irá remover todas as source.list e sources.list.d e criar as predefinidas,\n"
"irá executar o comando \"apt update\",\n"
"irá executar o comando \"apt install --fix-broken\",\n"
"irá executar o \"dpkg --configure -a\".\n"
"\n"
"Usar com precaução. Tem a certeza que quer continuar?"

